  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1174067">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1174067/" class="title-link">很不错的科学哲学入门书籍</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1174067"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/chenge/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1001000-16.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chenge/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">chenge</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-06-29"
      class="main-meta">2007-06-29 19:02:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1174067_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  科学哲学是对科学活动的反思。科学依赖于归纳，然而归纳虽然是实用的但是是不可靠的。然后有了波普尔的证伪主义，库恩的范式革命，拉卡托斯的研究纲领等等流派。  证伪主义的思路其实很简单，也很重要，是判定科学性的一个判据。就是看理论是否可能提出反例来，就是不能证伪的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1174067/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            河北科学技术出版社2002版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
